itself too seriousl","review_url":"https://broadwaybaby.com/shows/the-lady-boys-of-bangkok/835687"},{"id":149,"source_site":"Fringe Review","reviewer":"PL","rating_stars":4.0,"rating_raw":"Highly Recommended","excerpt":"Venue: Sabai Pavilion, Victoria Gardens, Grand Parade Back for the zillionth time, The Ladyboys of Bankok present their \"Mile High\" show, promising an unforgettable experience. The ladyboys are stunning as ever in a variety show that mixes mimed music, dancing, glitzy costumes, acrobatics and comedy.","review_url":"https://fringereview.co.uk/review/brighton-fringe/2009/the-ladyboys-of-bangkok/"}]}